{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And if I came to the city to pick up supplies for the workers, I was always with the horse, I don't-- didn't have a problem because nobody was checking papers from people who had-- it was a, a big lifesaver.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then we had-- there was an island on the Volga where it was a lot of wood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I had to prepare that island, housing and everything, for about 50 or 80 girls, and moving them and then the ice comes until the, the Volga freezes, we-- and we had to prepare wood for the city, and so on.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I made the mistake that, instead to go by, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] by horse, with my horse, I went by train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And by train, there was a check.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't have papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They arrested me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they sent me to the transit camp and to-- this was already in '44-- as a deserter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't have papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They didn't trust my stories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Syzran.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- there is a, a transit camp for regular people, and it-- for the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a prison on the transit camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I was interviewed by the-- by the chief criminal there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to tell the story, he told me, here you tell the truth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There with the-- with the commandant, you can say whatever you want to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow, I talk-- I told him the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know why they keep me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was my defense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] things didn't look good because they used to send those people, deserters-- and they had special battalions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They called them [NON-ENGLISH], which is for criminals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to go on the front.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
